    "code": "let a = 0, b = 0;\nfor (let i = 0; i < 16; i++) {\n  if (inputs[i].getValue()) a |= (1 << i);\n  if (inputs[i + 16].getValue()) b |= (1 << i);\n}\noutputs[0].setValue(a === b);\noutputs[1].setValue(a > b);\noutputs[2].setValue(a < b);"
